      "text": "PR 2 — 0025_drop_session_deprecated_columns.sql\n\nDROP COLUMN sessions.premise\nDROP COLUMN sessions.language\nDROP COLUMN sessions.tonal_frame\nDROP COLUMN sessions.engagement_profile\n\nGates (all must hold pre-drop):\n• ≥ 1 week prod stable on new flow\n• orphan sessions = 0\n• instance without campaign = 0\n• template with campaign = 0\n• campaign without session = 0",
